name: Heat core cushion
description: Handmade heat cushions made of pure cotton with natural cores. Available with spelt, rapeseed and green core. The heat pads can be heated in the oven at 100 degrees Celsius for about 10 minutes, and in the microwave at 800 watts for 90 seconds. Be very careful when removing it, as the pillow gets hot. Always make sure not to place the pillow on bare skin areas, but on garments. Children must not heat the product themselves, otherwise burns may occur! Pillows may only be heated by adults. Always supervise children in the handling of warming products! The pillows can also be placed in the fridge or briefly in the freezer to create a cooling effect. The rapeseed grains store both heat and cold at the longest, as they have a high oil content. In case of damage, do not reuse the pillow. Due to small grains, there is a risk of ingestion!

This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment. To be able to give love, I must first discard the (unconscious) conviction "I am not worth being loved" and begin to love myself. Only then can my love be visible in the outside.Physical effect:Radiaesthetic reviews showed that rose quartz positively affects relatively many frequencies. name: Rose Quartz Gemstone and healing stone/Rose Quartz Gemstone and Healing Stone/Mysticism/Bracelet/Spirituality/Mysticjewelry/Bracelet/Chip/
description: Rose Quartz Gemstone and Healing Stone BraceletSymbolic effect:The delicate pink ish-red colour symbolizes the still young rose bud, which is just about to unfold. For this reason, rose quartz can be recommended for all life situations in which a change or new beginning takes place:Rose Quartz Raw StoneRose Quartz Raw Stonee.g. at birth, puberty, pregnancy, career change, menopause, divorce, euthanasia. With "gentle determination" the rose quartz helps to unfold itself and to realize its true needs.He stands for unconditional love, which is without judging. This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment.
